xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/LxvRGM10paQ/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:122:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 25 Mar 2019 10:23:19 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"UpdraftPlus development news\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"updraft plus development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"UpdraftPlus\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"updraftplus update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=367357\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:862:\"<p>UpdraftPlus are happy to announce that we have been hard at work on a new update that we are now happy to share with you. The latest update of UpdraftPlus 1.16.10 includes several additional fixes and tweaks, including an all &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\">UpdraftPlus latest release now includes support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3421:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus are happy to announce that we have been hard at work on a new update that we are now happy to share with you. The latest update of UpdraftPlus 1.16.10 includes several additional fixes and tweaks, including an all new feature that gives support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Structured Query Language (SQL) is a standard computer language that is used for relational database management and data manipulation. SQL users typically use it to query, insert, update and modify data. Developing specific triggers that meet your SQL requirements can be a long term project with in depth processes that are unique to your specific database queries and requirements. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With UpdraftPlus 1.16.10, you will never have to worry about losing your valuable SQL triggers again should you suffer an issue with your site, such as a virus or a malicious hack. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So from now on, when you are using SQL to perform tasks such as update, analyse or retrieve data from your database, you can be assured that should the worst happen UpdraftPlus will allow you to restore the SQL triggers that you have developed, saving your valuable data, time and effort. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As well as this new feature, UpdraftPlus 1.16.10 also come with several other fixes and tweaks to make your UpdraftPlus experience even better. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We hope this new update will help improve your experience when using UpdraftPlus</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users. </span></p>\n<h4><b>UpdraftPlus 1.16.10</b></h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FEATURE: Added support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIX: Prevent the downloader UI being removed before its complete in the case of multi-archive sets (regression)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Refactor the restore code and use jobdata to save information about the restore rather than using $_POST data</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Automatically show the UpdraftClone admin UI for UpdraftClone developers for easier debugging</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Prevent a PHP notice with certain exclusion settings</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Add a mention of UpdraftClone in WPs PHP version notice and WooCommerces untested extensions notice</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Add 5.1 to the built-in list of available UpdraftClone WP versions</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\">UpdraftPlus latest release now includes support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:119:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:114:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"Access and upload images directly from Unsplash.com with the latest MetaSlider update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/yVIVBo5lZgg/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:118:\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 22 Mar 2019 09:44:41 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"MetaSlider\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"MetaSlider themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"MetaSlider update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=366353\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:858:\"<p>We are excited to announce that MetaSlider users now have the option of using the all new Unsplash.com library feature. When creating a new slideshow in MetaSlider, you now have the option to search and add images from a Unsplash.com &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\">Access and upload images directly from Unsplash.com with the latest MetaSlider update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7461:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are excited to announce that MetaSlider users now have the option of using the all new Unsplash.com library feature. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When creating a new slideshow in MetaSlider, you now have the option to search and add images from a Unsplash.com tab that behaves just like your very own personal massive media library. This incredibly handy new feature means there is no need to leave your WordPress page to search for images, and then try to remember where they are saved when adding them to your slideshow.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With our new feature, the search and upload of images with Upsplash.com can now all be done from within the MetaSlider plugin. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upsplash.com has over 850,000 completely free to use (do whatever you want with them) high-resolution photos that have been contributed by a large community of photographers from all over the world. Thousands of additional photos are added every day, with the types of images available covering a huge amount of topics and themes. With so much choice there is a very good chance that Upsplash.com has the type of photos you are looking for. </span></p>\n<p><b>How to use the new Upsplash.com feature in MetaSlider</b></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366366\" style=\"width: 792px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366366\" class=\"wp-image-366366\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"782\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8.jpg 1351w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-300x95.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-768x243.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-1024x324.jpg 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-1080x341.jpg 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-510x161.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 782px) 100vw, 782px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366366\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Just select Add Slide and click on the Unsplash Library tab.</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366365\" style=\"width: 766px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a style=\"font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366365\" class=\"wp-image-366365 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"756\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9.jpg 756w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9-300x107.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9-510x182.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 756px) 100vw, 756px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366365\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Use the Search unsplash.com search option to find the images you want.</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366364\" style=\"width: 523px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366364\" class=\"wp-image-366364 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"513\" height=\"725\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10.jpg 513w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10-212x300.jpg 212w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10-510x721.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366364\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Select your favourite and click Add to slideshow&#8221;.</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366362\" style=\"width: 1146px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366362\" class=\"wp-image-366362\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1136\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12.jpg 1551w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-300x132.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-768x337.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-1024x450.jpg 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-1080x474.jpg 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-510x224.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1136px) 100vw, 1136px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366362\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Unsplash.com image you added automatically uploads to your library and is added to your new slideshow. It really is that easy!</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366361\" style=\"width: 983px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366361\" class=\"wp-image-366361 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"973\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13.jpg 973w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13-300x131.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13-768x335.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13-510x223.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 973px) 100vw, 973px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366361\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Slideshow preview</p></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br />\nMetaSlider is available for download </span><a href=\"https://metaslider.com/upgrade/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Sign up and download it to your WordPress website today and let the fun begin. If you have any comments about the latest update, be sure to let us know in the comments below.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users:</span></p>\n<p><b>Change log</b></p>\n<p><b>3.12.0  2019/MAR/18</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Sets a default theme on a newly created slideshow</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Adds various trivial code quality fixes</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIX: Fixes a bug where Nivo and Coin Slider did not ship with the plugin</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FEATURE: Adds access to the Unsplash.com image library</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\">Access and upload images directly from Unsplash.com with the latest MetaSlider update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:115:\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:110:\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"UpdraftPlus release new 1.16.8 update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/VBNX1DYUTbE/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base